name: brainbeez.com
overview:
Brainbeez.com is an organization working for the benefits of the students, employees and job seekers who are actively looking for improving their credentials, searching jobs, looking for career guidance and need interview preparation material on various subjects.

Brainbeez.com provide

  1. Free online certification (Certificate is directly sent to your email address)
  2. Free interview prep and study guides material
  3. Free career counseling
  4. Free practice test on various competitive exams like GRE, GMAT, TOEFL, ICET, EAMCET, GATE etc.,
  5. Job Search
  6. Blogs & Forums
